resources.string: ServicePlace seeks to create services in currently under-served areas using technology to connect the people we serve - using a holistic method to extend compassion and awareness.
Born 2 Help is a volunteer-based group, saw the light of the day in the year 2015 with an aim to provide better living to children across slums in India.
Born-2-Help provides daily food delivery to elderly and disadvantaged people.
Born for a reason, we have responsibility towards our society and the people who belongs to this society.Let\'s help them whenever needed.
